definitions.definition: An alpine style of wooden building with a sloping roof and overhanging eaves .
A recreational lodge or small house within the grounds of a country club , resort , clubhouse or other recreational space, used for events , staycations and social gatherings.

main_definition: An alpine style of wooden building with a sloping roof and overhanging eaves . [from late 18th c.]
